\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Landlord}: [Landlord Name], residing at [Landlord Address] (``Landlord'')
    \item \textbf{Tenant}: [Tenant Name], residing at [Tenant Address] (``Tenant'')
\end{itemize}

\subsection*{Property}
The property to which this Agreement applies is located at [Property Address] (the ``Property'').

\subsection*{Deposit Details}
The Tenant has paid a deposit of \textbf{[Deposit Amount]} (the ``Deposit'') to the Landlord on [Date of Payment]. The Deposit is held as security for the performance of the Tenantâ€™s obligations under the Tenancy Agreement dated [Tenancy Agreement Date].

